column22: Observations
Mega 1: problems during deployment, needed 1h 15min to fix while ship was drifting of the course due to weather conditions
Mega 2: during the 1h 15min of delayed Mega 1 deployment, Mega 2 was trawling with 2knots
wind picked up during middle of trawl to 19.9 knots for about 15 minutes
caught a massive rope island 4*5 - 50lbs (obs from Julia: it is a ghostnet - pic provided by them in Dec'16). It was in the wing so not considered part of the sample
